name: NEW KRYPTO KICKS - Series 01, #10 - "Swamp Beast" by Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
description:
[Paint pen and metallic marker on reclaimed cardboard with digital embellishments and color.]

My brothers and I grew up just a few miles from a nuclear powerplant, and we would often visit the park that was built around the reactor and even swim in the waters of the artificial lake that was created on site for PR purposes... The reactor was eventually demolished, but not before its legacy oozed into the swampy marshlands---changing and twisting the surrounding plant and animal life...until one fateful night when IT was born... ---Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
